                "id": 90,
                "name": "Saukko"
            },
            "notes": "So far it goes as described in the description.\r\nFor soldier it goes as Primary -> Secondary -> Grenades -> Knife\r\nFor medic it goes as Primary -> Secondary -> Grenades -> Syringe (obviously syringe doesn't kill anybody so why not knife after it?)\r\nFor engineer it goes as Primary -> Secondary -> Grenades -> Pliers (another silly joke here :D, I would rather set knife)\r\nFor field ops it goes as Primary -> Secondary -> Grenades -> Airstrike canister (I don't know about this but I would rather take knife out even in this situation?)\r\nFor covert ops it goes as Primary -> Secondary -> Grenades -> Smoke grenade (Knife would be more logical than Satchel charge?)\r\n\r\nMy personal opinion into this is: Primary -> Secondary -> Grenades -> Knife OR Primary -> Secondary -> Knife -> ...\r\n\r\nI would like to hear other people's opinion on this.\r\n\r\n-*S",
